urg, Germany\n| Clay\n| {{flagicon|TCH}} Ivan Lendl\n| 1\u20136, 3\u20136, 3\u20136\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Win\n| 8\u20139\n| Jul 1987\n| [[Mercedes Cup|Stuttgart]], Germany\n| Clay\n| {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Jan Gunnarsson]]\n| 6\u20130, 6\u20132\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Win\n| 9\u20139\n| Jul 1987\n| [[Dutch Open (tennis)|Hilversum]], Netherlands\n| Clay\n| {{flagicon|ARG}} [[Guillermo P\u00e9rez Rold\u00e1n]]\n| 6\u20134, 1\u20136, 6\u20133, 6\u20132\n|- \n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Loss\n| 9\u201310\n| Aug 1987\n| [[Generali Open|Kitzb\u00fchel]], Austria\n| Clay\n| {{flagicon|ESP}}  [[Emilio S\u00e1nchez]]\n| 4\u20136, 1\u20136, 6\u20134, 1\u20136\n|-\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Loss\n| 9\u201311\n| Feb 1988\n| [[ABN AMRO World Tennis Tournament|Rotterdam]], Netherlands\n| Carpet (i)\n| {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Stefan Edberg]]\n| 6\u20137<sup>(5\u20137)</sup>, 2\u20136\n|-\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Loss\n| 9\u201312\n| Mar 1988\n| [[Verizon Tennis Challenge|Orlando]], U.S.\n| Hard\n| {{flagicon|URS}} [[Andrei Chesnokov]]\n| 6\u20137<sup>(6\u20138)</sup>, 1\u20136\n|- bgcolor=#ffea5c\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Win\n| 10\u201312\n| Sep 1988\n| [[Tennis at the 1988 Summer Olympics|Olympic Games]], Seoul\n| Hard\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Tim Mayotte]]\n| 3\u20136, 6\u20132, 6\u20134, 6\u20132\n|- bgcolor=\"#f3e6d7\"\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Loss\n| 10\u201313\n| Jan 1989\n| [[Australian Open]], Melbourne\n| Hard\n| {{flagicon|TCH}} Ivan Lendl\n| 2\u20136, 2\u20136, 2\u20136\n|- style=\"background:#e9e9e9;\"\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Win\n| 11\u201313\n| Mar 1989\n| [[Indian Wells Masters|Indian Wells]], U.S.\n| Hard\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} Yannick Noah\n| 3\u20136, 2\u20136, 6\u20131, 6\u20132, 6\u20133\n|}\n\n===Doubles: 12 (9 titles, 3 runner-ups)===\n{|class=wikitable style=font-size:97%\n!Legend\n|-bgcolor=f3e6d7\n|Grand Slam (0\u20130)\n|-bgcolor=ffffcc\n|Year-end championships \u2013 ATP (1\u20130)\n|-bgcolor=e9e9e9\n|Grand Prix Super Series (1\u20131)\n|-\n|ATP Grand Prix (7\u20132)\n|}\n{|class=\"sortable wikitable\" \n!style=\"width:40px\"|Result\n!No.\n!Date\n!Tournament\n!Surface\n!Partner\n!Opponents\n!Score\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Win\n| 1.\n| 28 July 1986\n| [[Dutch Open (tennis)|Hilversum]], Netherlands\n| Clay\n| {{flagicon|TCH}} [[Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd]]\n| {{flagicon|NED}} [[Tom Nijssen]] <br /> {{flagicon|NED}} [[Johan Vekemans]]\n| 6\u20134, 6\u20132\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Win\n| 2.\n| 6 October 1986\n| [[Grand Prix de Tennis de Toulouse|Toulouse]], France\n| Hard (i)\n| {{flagicon|TCH}} Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd\n| {{flagicon|SUI}} [[Jakob Hlasek]] <br /> {{flagicon|TCH}} [[Pavel Slo\u017eil]]\n| 6\u20132, 3\u20136, 6\u20134\n|- style=\"background:#e9e9e9;\"\n| bgcolor=98fb98|Winner\n| 3.\n| 27 April 1987\n| [[German Open Tennis Championships|Hamburg]], Germany\n| Clay\n| {{flagicon|TCH}} Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd\n| {{flagicon|SUI}} [[Claudio Mezzadri]] <br /> {{flagicon|USA}} [[Jim Pugh]]\n| 4\u20136, 7\u20136, 6\u20132\n|- style=\"background:#e9e9e9;\"\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Loss\n| 1.\n| 11 May 1987\n| [[Italian Open (tennis)|Rome]], Italy\n| Clay\n| {{flagicon|TCH}} Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Guy Forget]] <br /> {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Yannick Noah]]\n| 2\u20136, 7\u20136, 3\u20136\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Win\n| 4.\n| 27 July 1987\n| Hilversum, Netherlands\n| Clay\n| {{flagicon|POL}} [[Wojciech Fibak]]\n| {{flagicon|NED}} Tom Nijssen <br /> {{flagicon|NED}} [[Johan Vekemans]]\n| 7\u20136, 5\u20137, 6\u20132\n|- \n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Loss\n| 2.\n| 3 August 1987\n| [[Austrian Open Kitzb\u00fchel|Kitzb\u00fchel]], Austria\n| Clay\n| {{flagicon|TCH}} Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Sergio Casal]] <br /> {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Emilio S\u00e1nchez]]\n| 6\u20137, 6\u20137\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Win\n| 5.\n| 10 August 1987\n| [[Prague Open (1987\u20131999)|Prague]], Czechoslovakia\t\n| Clay\n| {{flagicon|TCH}} Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd\n| {{flagicon|TCH}} [[Stanislav Birner]] <br /> {{flagicon|TCH}} [[Jaroslav Navr\u00e1til (tennis)|Jaroslav Navr\u00e1til]]\n| 6\u20133, 6\u20137, 6\u20133\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Win\n| 6.\n| 21 September 1987\n| [[Barcelona Open (tennis)|Barcelona]], Spain\n| Clay\n| {{flagicon|TCH}} Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd\n| {{flagicon|ARG}} [[Javier Frana]] <br /> {{flagicon|ARG}} [[Christian Miniussi]]\n| 6\u20131, 6\u20132\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Win\n| 7.\n| 9 November 1987\n| [[Wembley Championships|Wembley]], U.K.\n| Carpet (i)\n| {{flagicon|TCH}} Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Ken Flach]] <br /> {{flagicon|USA}} [[Robert Seguso]]\n| 7\u20135, 6\u20134\n|- bgcolor=\"ffffcc\"\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Win\n| 8.\n| 7 December 1987\n| [[ATP World Tour Finals|Masters Doubles]], London\n| Carpet (i)\n| {{flagicon|TCH}} Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd\n| {{flagicon|USA}} Ken Flach <br /> {{flagicon|USA}} Robert Seguso\n| 6\u20134, 7\u20135, 6\u20137<sup>(5\u20137)</sup>, 6\u20133\n|- \n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Loss\n| 3.\n| 15 February 1988\n| [[Milan Indoor|Milan]], Italy\n| Carpet (i)\n| {{flagicon|TCH}} Tom\u00e1\u0161 \u0160m\u00edd\n| {{flagicon|FRG}} [[Boris Becker]] <br /> {{flagicon|FRG}} [[Eric Jelen]]\n| 3\u20136, 3\u20136\n|- \n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Win\n| 9.\n| 6 February 1989\n| [[Rotterdam Open|Rotterdam]], Netherlands\n| Carpet (i)\n| {{flagicon|TCH}} [[Milan \u0160rejber]]\n| {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Jan Gunnarsson]] <br /> {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Magnus Gustafsson]]\n| 7\u20136, 6\u20130\n|}\n\n==Grand Slam singles performance timeline==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#efefef\"\n! Tournament !! 1983 !! 1984 !! 1985 !! 1986 !! 1987 !! 1988 !! 1989 !! 1990 !! Career SR !! Career Win-Loss\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | Australian Open\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|1R\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|2R\n|align=\"center\" |A\n|align=\"center\" |NH\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#ffebcd;\"|QF\n|align=\"center\" |A\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#D8BFD8;\" | F\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|4R\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | 0 / 5\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" |12\u20135\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | French Open\n|align=\"center\" |A\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|1R\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|3R\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|2R\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:yellow;\"|SF\n|align=\"center\" |A\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|1R\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|1R\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | 0 / 6\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" |8\u20136\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | [[The Championships, Wimbledon|Wimbledon]]\n|align=\"center\" |A\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|2R\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|1R\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#ffebcd;\"|QF\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|3R\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:yellow;\"|SF\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|3R\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|2R\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | 0 / 7\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" |15\u20137\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | [[US Open (tennis)|US Open]]\n|align=\"center\" |A\n|align=\"center\" |A\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|2R\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#D8BFD8;\" | F\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#ffebcd;\"|QF\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|3R\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|3R\n|align=\"center\" |A\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | 0 / 5\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#EFEF